<div class="com-share" data-id="5853" data-title="《收购盈方体育，王健林这次做了一笔好生意》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/5853/medium/5853.jpg?1436690822" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/5853" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
